    <div class="p-3 rounded mt-3" style="background:var(--pm-surface-2);font-size:12px"><i class="bi bi-lightbulb text-warning me-1"></i> <strong>Insight:</strong> Mombasa branch has slower collection times (DSO 34 vs 22). Consider implementing automated payment reminders for coastal clients.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer"><button class="pm-btn" (click)="closeModal()">Close</button></div>
</div>
